texts.content: {"text":"1. Qoof. Ulug` Qur'on ila qasam.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,32]}]}

{"text":"2. Balki, ularga o`zlaridan ogohlantiruvchi kelganidan ajablandilar va kofirlar: \n«Bu ajib narsa-ku?» – dedilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,112]}]}

{"text":"3. O`lib, tuproq bo`lganimizdan keyin ham-a? \nBu qaytish (aqldan) uzoq.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,71]}]}

{"text":"4. Haqiqatan, Biz ularni yer kamaytirayotganini bildik va Bizning huzurimizda saqlovchi kitob bor.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,98]}]}

{"text":"5. Aniqki, ularga haq kelganda, uni yolg`onga chiqardilar. Bas, ular iztirobli ishdadirlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,91]}]}

{"text":"6. Ustilaridagi osmonga nazar solmaydilarmi? Uni qanday bino qilibmiz va ziynatlabmiz? \nVa (holbuki), uning teshiklari ham yo`q?!","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,129]}]}

{"text":"7. Va yerni cho`zib qo`ydik, unga tog`larni tashladik va unda turli go`zal juftlarni o`stirdik.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,95]}]}

{"text":"8. (Robbisiga) qaytuvchi har bir bandaga \nko`rgazma va eslatma qilib...","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,71]}]}

{"text":"9. Va osmondan baraka suvini tushirdik hamda u bilan bog`-rog`larni va don hosilini o`stirdik.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,94]}]}

{"text":"10. Va zich mevali shingillari bor xurmolarni ham.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,50]}]}

{"text":"11. Bandalarga rizq qilib. Va u (yomg`ir) bilan \no`lgan shaharni tiriltirdik. Shunday bo`ladir \n(qabrdan) chiqish ham.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,118]}]}

{"text":"12. Ulardan avval Nuh qavmi, quduq sohiblari va Samud yolg`onga chiqarganlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,77]}]}

{"text":"13. Va Od, Fir'avn, Lut birodarlari.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,36]}]}

{"text":"14. Va daraxtzor egalari va Tubba' qavmi — barchalari Payg`ambarlarni yolg`onga chiqarganlar. Bas, (azob) va'dam haq bo`ldi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,124]}]}

{"text":"15. Avvalgi yaratishga ojiz bo`l-dikmi? Yo`q! \nUlar yangidan yaratilishga shubhadadirlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,89]}]}

{"text":"16. Albatta, insonni Biz yaratganmiz va uning nafsi nimani vasvasa qilishini ham bilurmiz. \nVa Biz unga jon tomiridan ham yaqinmiz.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,131]}]}

{"text":"17. Vaqtiki ikki kutib oluvchi o`ngda \nva chapda o`tirgan hollarida kutib olurlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,82]}]}

{"text":"18. Biror so`z aytmas, \nmagar huzurida hoziru nozir borlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,59]}]}

{"text":"19. O`limning mastligi (talvasasi) haqiqat bo`lib keldi. Sen qochib yurgan narsa shuldir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,89]}]}

{"text":"20. Va sur ham chalindi. Bu, qo`rqitilgan kundir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,49]}]}

{"text":"21. Va har bir jon haydaguvchi va \nguvohlik beruvchi bilan keldi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,65]}]}

{"text":"22. Albatta, sen bundan g`aflatda eding. \nBas, Biz sening pardangni ochdik va \nbugun ko`zing o`tkirdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,103]}]}

{"text":"23. Va uning «yaqini»: \n«Mana bu mendagi tayyor narsa», dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,61]}]}

{"text":"24. Har bir qaysarni, \nkofirni jahannamga tashlang!","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,51]}]}

{"text":"25. Yaxshilikni man qiluvchini, \ntajovuzkorni, shak keltiruvchini.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,66]}]}

{"text":"26. Alloh bilan birga boshqani iloh qilib olganni shiddatli azobga tashlang!","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,76]}]}

{"text":"27. Uning «yaqini»: \n«Robbimiz, uni men tug`yonga ketkazganim yo`q, lekin uning o`zi uzoq zalolatda bo`ldi», der.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,113]}]}

{"text":"28. U zot dedi: \n«Mening huzurimda tortishmanglar, \nsizlarga azob va'dasini taqdim qiluvdim.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,92]}]}

{"text":"29. Mening huzurimda gap o`zgarmas va \nMen bandalarga zulm qilguvchi emasman».","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,78]}]}

{"text":"30. Bugun jahannamga: «To`ldingmi?» desak, \nu: «Yana qo`shimcha bormi?» der.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,76]}]}

{"text":"31. Va jannat taqvodorlarga uzoq bo`lmagan joyga yaqinlashtirildi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,66]}]}

{"text":"32. Bu — sizga va'da qilingan narsadir. \nHar bir sertavbaga va saqlovchiga.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,75]}]}

{"text":"33. Rohmandan g`oyibona qo`rqqan va \nsalomat qalb ila kelgan kimsaga.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,69]}]}

{"text":"34. «Unga salomat bo`lgan holda kiringiz. \nBu — mangulik kunidir» (deyilur).","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,76]}]}

{"text":"35. U yerda nima xohlasalar, ularniki. \nVa huzurimizda ziyodasi bor.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,68]}]}

{"text":"36. Ulardan avval, ulardan ko`ra kuchliroq 
asr(avlod)lardan qanchasini halok qildik. 
«Qochadigan joy bormi?» deb yurtma-yurt 
kezib chiqdilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,144]}]}

{"text":"37. Albatta, bunda qalbi borlarga va \nzehn bilan quloq osganlarga eslatma bordir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,81]}]}

{"text":"38. Albatta, osmonlaru yerni va ularning orasidagi narsalarni olti kunda yaratdik. \nVa Bizni charchoq tutmadi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,110]}]}

{"text":"39. Ularning aytayotganlariga sabr qil va Robbingga quyosh chiqishi va botishidan avval hamdu tasbih ayt.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,105]}]}

{"text":"40. Kechasida ham Unga tasbih ayt. \nVa sajdadan keyin ham.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,58]}]}

{"text":"41. Nido qiluvchi yaqin joydan nido qilgan \nkunda quloq os.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,59]}]}

{"text":"42. U kunda qichqiriqni haq ila eshiturlar. \nAna o`sha, chiqish kunidir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,72]}]}

{"text":"43. Albatta, Biz tiriltirurmiz, o`ldirurmiz. \nVa qaytish ham Bizgadir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,70]}]}

{"text":"44. U kunda ustlaridagi yer yorilib, \nshoshib chiqurlar. Ana o`sha, \nBiz uchun oson to`plashdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,96]}]}

{"text":"45. Ularning aytganlarini Biz biluvchimiz. 
Sen ularning ustidagi jabbor emassan. 
Bas, Qur'on ila azob va'damdan 
qo`rqqanlarni ogohlantir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,140]}]}

{"text":"قٓ ۚ وَٱلْقُرْءَانِ ٱلْمَجِيدِ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,30]}]}

{"text":"بَلْ عَجِبُوٓا۟ أَن جَآءَهُم مُّنذِرٌۭ مِّنْهُمْ فَقَالَ ٱلْكَٰفِرُونَ هَٰذَا شَىْءٌ عَجِيبٌ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,93]}]}

{"text":"أَءِذَا مِتْنَا وَكُنَّا تُرَابًۭا ۖ ذَٰلِكَ رَجْعٌۢ بَعِيدٌۭ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,61]}]}

{"text":"قَدْ عَلِمْنَا مَا تَنقُصُ ٱلْأَرْضُ مِنْهُمْ ۖ وَعِندَنَا كِتَٰبٌ حَفِيظٌۢ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,75]}]}

{"text":"بَلْ كَذَّبُوا۟ بِٱلْحَقِّ لَمَّا جَآءَهُمْ فَهُمْ فِىٓ أَمْرٍۢ مَّرِيجٍ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,73]}]}

{"text":"أَفَلَمْ يَنظُرُوٓا۟ إِلَى ٱلسَّمَآءِ فَوْقَهُمْ كَيْفَ بَنَيْنَٰهَا وَزَيَّنَّٰهَا وَمَا لَهَا مِن فُرُوجٍۢ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,109]}]}

{"text":"وَٱلْأَرْضَ مَدَدْنَٰهَا وَأَلْقَيْنَا فِيهَا رَوَٰسِىَ وَأَنۢبَتْنَا فِيهَا مِن كُلِّ زَوْجٍۭ بَهِيجٍۢ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,103]}]}

{"text":"تَبْصِرَةًۭ وَذِكْرَىٰ لِكُلِّ عَبْدٍۢ مُّنِيبٍۢ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,48]}]}

{"text":"وَنَزَّلْنَا مِنَ ٱلسَّمَآءِ مَآءًۭ مُّبَٰرَكًۭا فَأَنۢبَتْنَا بِهِۦ جَنَّٰتٍۢ وَحَبَّ ٱلْحَصِيدِ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,99]}]}

{"text":"وَٱلنَّخْلَ بَاسِقَٰتٍۢ لَّهَا طَلْعٌۭ نَّضِيدٌۭ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,48]}]}

{"text":"رِّزْقًۭا لِّلْعِبَادِ ۖ وَأَحْيَيْنَا بِهِۦ بَلْدَةًۭ مَّيْتًۭا ۚ كَذَٰلِكَ ٱلْخُرُوجُ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,87]}]}

{"text":"كَذَّبَتْ قَبْلَهُمْ قَوْمُ نُوحٍۢ وَأَصْحَٰبُ ٱلرَّسِّ وَثَمُودُ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,65]}]}

{"text":"وَأَصْحَٰبُ ٱلْأَيْكَةِ وَقَوْمُ تُبَّعٍۢ ۚ كُلٌّۭ كَذَّبَ ٱلرُّسُلَ فَحَقَّ وَعِيدِ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.929411768913269,0.7764706015586853,0.556862771511078]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,84]}]}
